  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"media-1.7.0-beta01\" data-text=\"Version 1.7.0-beta01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.7.0-beta01</h3>\n<p>November 1, 2023</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.media:media:1.7.0-beta01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/7d3ac1ab1206c01fae3ebb500b5b942636070155..e3ffd7948030a769c857b8c629e0079c54b730ad/media/media\">Version 1.7.0-beta01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix potential memory leak of <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">MediaBrowserService</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">MediaBrowserServiceCompat</code>. <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/37137738\">b/37137738</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">IllegalStateException</code> caused by returning null from <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">MediaBrowserService.onLoadChildren</code> on older Android versions.</li>\n</ul>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/7d3ac1ab1206c01fae3ebb500b5b942636070155..e3ffd7948030a769c857b8c629e0079c54b730ad/media/media"
